Nyasaye ma ng’ado ni ji duto bura


1  A Ruoth Nyasaye, in Nyasaye machulo kuor.

Nyiswa kaka ichalo!


2  In e jang’ad bura ni ji duto.

Koro a malo mondo imi josunga gima giromogo!


3  A Nyasaye, joricho biro bedo mamor nyaka karang’o?


4  Joma timbegi mono biro sungore kendo kawore

kuom kinde marom nade?


5  Ginyono jogi, yaye Nyasaye.

Ee, githiro oganda miseyiero.


6  Ginego mond liete gi nyithi kiye,

kaachiel gi jopinje mamoko modak e pinywa


7  Giwacho niya, “Nyasaye ok newa.

Adier, Nyasach Jakobo ok dew gima watimo!”


8  Un joga, ere kaka unyalo bedo joma ofuwo momemore kamano?

Unupuonjru karang’o?


9  Uparo ni Nyasaye mane ochueyo it ok winj koso?

Koso ng’ama nochueyo wang’ donge neno?


10  En ema orito ogendini! Donge okumogi?

Koso ng’ama puonjo dhano nyalo bedo maonge gi rieko adier?


11  

Nyasaye ong’eyo ni paro mag dhano nono.


12  Nyasaye, ng’at ma ichiko, kendo ipuonjo chikeni, en jahawi,


13  nikech imiye yueyo e kinde mag chandruok

ka joricho to ichikonigi obadho.


14  Nyasaye ok nojwang’ joge owuon kendo ok nowegi.


15  Bura nochak ong’ad kare kendo, mi ji makare duto noyiego.


16  Onge ng’at mane ochung’ mondo okonya kuom joma richo.

Adier, onge ng’at mane ochwaka kuom joma timbegi mono.


17  Kuom mano, ka dine Nyasaye we konya,

to dine asedhi piyopiyo e piny ma ok wuoe.


18  Pile kane aneno ni tienda dwaro kier,

to in Nyasaye ne ikonya gi herani mosiko.


19  Ka an gi parruok kendo kihondko omaka,

to ikueyo chunya, kendo imiya bedo mamor.


20  In ibet mabor gi jong’ad buch amwor,

ma miyo timbe maricho nenore ka gik ma chik oyiego,


21  kendo ma chokore mondo otim ni joma kare timbe mamono,

mi ng’ad ni joma onge ketho buch tho.


22  To in Ruoth Nyasaye, ema ibedona kar konyruok.

In e Nyasaye ma obedona lwanda ma ageng’orae.


23  Ibiro kumo jogo kuom timbegi mamono,

mi itiekgi nikech richogi.

Ee, in Ruoth Nyasachwa, ibiro tiekogi.

